data.description: NEW PRICE! This property is located on 10 wooded acres with 1895 SF of space, three bedrooms, chicken cage, additional house, pool and much more! Master suite is located on the upper level of home and has been freshly painted. However, the upper floor is ground level as you pull into the drive. Large master bath with shower. The main floor has a soaring 17' vaulted in the carpeted Great room with lots of natural lighting. Kitchen has electric range, refrigerator, dishwasher and oak cabinetry. The large dining area is an extension of the kitchen. The second bedroom has a supersized walk-in closet. There is a second bath with tub on this level as well. Also features an 8x17 furnace room with laundry area. Plus, an 8x20 storage room. This property has no basement. If you like living private, this is a wonderful spot. Lots of land to make it your own. Don’t wait to get your showing today! Motivated Seller! Priced for a quick sale.
